+# 0273-r1 — Laboratory framework reuse audit
+
+This release records the mandatory reuse audit before adding laboratory contracts or providers.
+
+The repository already owns the complete surrounding chain:
+
+```text
+durable candidate
+-> orientation
+-> Scheduler and policies
+-> specialist/deliberation routes
+-> SQL / E5 / Qdrant
+-> EventBus / PassiveSupervisor / Cell Lens
+-> reviewed GitHub return
+```
+
+The next phase may add only the missing versioned laboratory identity, bounded visit contracts, provider membrane and capability binding in the existing registry.
+
+No runtime capability is added.
